title: Catfish Noodle Jug Orange Pack of 5 UNRIGGED Made in The USA
description: This is a package of 5 NEW custom made UNRIGGED Catfish Noddle Jugs. As pictured they are hi-visibility Orange floats. They are built on a 1/2" PVC center tube that are 12" long. They DO NOT include any terminal tackle i.e. hook, line or sinker. They are built with an included galvanized eye bolt to attach your terminal tackle to. This allows the fishermen to attach line of a length and hook size for their own liking and for their specific fishing conditions. Proudly Made In The USA.
